<TEXT>
an israeli teenager who dreamed of jewisharab 
coexistence and befriended many arabs in the west bank was slain 
by a palestinian acquaintance after she refused to get him a gun 
police said wednesday 
the palestinian whose name was not released confessed to the 
slaying of 18yearold ziva goldovsky and reconstructed the crime 
for police said investigator uri weisskoop 
ms goldovskys charred remains were found aug 15 in a field 
near the west bank town el bireh weisskoop said her assailant 
choked her from behind and struck her repeatedly with a large stone 
before he and an accomplice set the corpse on fire 
ms goldovsky became the fifth israeli to die in the 9monthold 
palestinian uprising the palestinian death toll has reached 259 
israel radio described ms goldovsky an immigrant from the 
soviet union as an activist in the leftwing mapam party who 
could be found at most propalestinian demonstrations 
ms goldovsky a resident of the tel aviv suburb of holon was 
engaged to a palestinian from the west bank city of hebron friends 
of the victim told the associated press last month 
ms goldovskys fiance who has a police record is in custody 
on robbery charges but is not a suspect in the slaying police said 
on aug 13 ms goldovsky and a palestinian acquaintance went 
for a walk near el bireh and began to argue israel radio said 
the man started hitting her and shouted why do you dress so 
immodestly the report said 
dont hit me she said even my parents dont beat me 
the man then accused her of being an informer for israels shin 
bet security service when she denied this he said prove it 
get me a pistol 
she refused saying i should get you a gun so you can kill 
young jewish boys and girls 
the man again slapped ms goldovsky and then choked her 
he took us to the place where he killed her weisskoop was 
quoted as telling the radio he approached her from behind 
choked her and laid her on the ground 
then he hit her with a large stone about 50 yards from the 
site of the killing he and a friend burned the body and this is how 
she was found 
one of ms goldovskys jewish friends speaking on condition of 
anonymity said last month she often hitchhiked to the west bank 
and formed friendships with many palestinians 
the friend said ms goldovsky dreamed of jewisharab 
coexistence 
ziva would have continued her road of coexistence even if she 
knew what her end would be he said 
</TEXT>
