cosmonauts just returned from a problemplagued 
space mission described cramped quarters food and water shortages 
and equipment problems but did not address questions about their 
performance a tass dispatch indicated today 
the government newspaper izvestia had suggested wednesday that 
the commander of the soyuz tm5 capsule stranded in orbit for a 
