chryslers frontdrive configuration does limit towing capacity 
however with the standard 25liter fourcylinder the voyager can 
handle up to 2000 lbs with the v6 and class ii framemounted 
trailer hitch it can take 2750 lbs 
in contrast many reardrive vans can handle bigger loads 
consumer reports says 198486 plymouth voyagers have ranked 
average or above average in reports of trouble 
